description: This file implements backend APIs for managing WiFi data within a larger software project, specifically in the context of a TR-069 based device management system. It includes functions to get and set string parameters related to managed WiFi data, and contains licensing, module description, and API documentation headers.

methods.name: ULONG Lanconfig_GetParamStringValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pValue,ULONG * pUlSize)
methods.description: Retrieves string parameter values, specifically handling 'ManagedWiFiData' parameter.

methods.name: BOOL Lanconfig_SetParamStringValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pString)
methods.description: Sets string parameter values; in particular, processes 'ManagedWiFiData' parameter by calling unpackAndProcessManagedWifiData.
